    <item>
      <title>Asterisk: пишем CDR в базу данных MySQL</title>
      <link>https://ealebed.github.io/posts/asterisk-%D0%BF%D0%B8%D1%88%D0%B5%D0%BC-cdr-%D0%B2-%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%B7%D1%83-%D0%B4%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D1%85-mysql/</link>
